26#define SIG_ATOMIC_TYPE "int"
27
28#define INT8_TYPE "signed char"
29#define INT16_TYPE "short int"
30#define INT32_TYPE "int"
31#define INT64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long int" : "long long int")
32#define UINT8_TYPE "unsigned char"
33#define UINT16_TYPE "short unsigned int"
34#define UINT32_TYPE "unsigned int"
35#define UINT64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long unsigned int" : "long long unsigned int")
36
37#define INT_LEAST8_TYPE "signed char"
38#define INT_LEAST16_TYPE "short int"
39#define INT_LEAST32_TYPE "int"
40#define INT_LEAST64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long int" : "long long int")
41#define UINT_LEAST8_TYPE "unsigned char"
42#define UINT_LEAST16_TYPE "short unsigned int"
43#define UINT_LEAST32_TYPE "unsigned int"
44#define UINT_LEAST64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long unsigned int" : "long long unsigned int")
45
46#ifdef CHAR_FAST8
47#define INT_FAST8_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "int" : "signed char")
48#else
49#define INT_FAST8_TYPE "int"
50#endif
51#ifdef SHORT_FAST16
52#define INT_FAST16_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "int" : "short int")
53#else
54#define INT_FAST16_TYPE "int"
55#endif
56#define INT_FAST32_TYPE "int"
57#define INT_FAST64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long int" : "long long int")
58#ifdef CHAR_FAST8
59#define UINT_FAST8_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "unsigned int" : "unsigned char")
60#else
61#define UINT_FAST8_TYPE "unsigned int"
62#endif
63#ifdef SHORT_FAST16
64#define UINT_FAST16_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "unsigned int" : "short unsigned int")
65#else
66#define UINT_FAST16_TYPE "unsigned int"
67#endif
68#define UINT_FAST32_TYPE "unsigned int"
69#define UINT_FAST64_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long unsigned int" : "long long unsigned int")
70
71#define INTPTR_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long int" : "int")
72#define UINTPTR_TYPE (LONG_TYPE_SIZE == 64 ? "long unsigned int" : "unsigned int")
73
